    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Setting up Spree to play with Amazon S3]]></title>
    <link href="http://davwood.github.io/blog/2014/03/22/setting-up-spree-to-play-wth-amazon-s3/"/>
    <updated>2014-03-22T10:23:01+11:00</updated>
